spirit:component.spirit:name: kth_axi_rni_static
spirit:component.spirit:description: A memory mapped peripheral via ARM AMBA AXI4 Bus implementing functionality for Network Resource Interface for KTH Nostrum Network-on-Chip (NoC) Message Passing Mechanism (MPM) for Multi-Processor System-on-Chip (MPSoC). The implementation describes the static version of the NoC in which the RNI processes and process mapping and channels are set at design time thus static
